{
  "text": "\u2022 The GP Patient Survey can be used to provide robust comparisons between healthcare providers such as practices. [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] \u2022 Improving the experience of patients in low-scoring practices will improve the quality of care provided to white patients, and reduce ethnic group differences in patient experience.",
  "correct_citation": {
    "[CITATION_1]": "11352298",
